{"tid":562720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反共，親共，親英，港獨，都係港豬思想","createTime":"2018-02-16T07:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T09:18:16.000Z","uid":149978,"like":22,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1364375cf07aed83acb8a15e5352017357e0a4e8","tid":562720,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T07:33:03.000Z","msg":"反共：明知比共產黨食住，都唔肯刷共產黨鞋。你反共，共反你。<br />\n<br />\n親共：明知共產黨獨裁，黨內貪腐勁，管理混亂，都要親共。看下歷史，共產黨做的野：反右運動、大躍進、文革、六四、簡體字運動。<br />\n<br />\n親英：明知歸英不可能。同埋英殖香港時，英國人歧視香港人都好嚴重。自己諗下，以前日不落帝國，點解有幾多前英國殖民地，都選擇脫英獨立？<br />\n<br />\n港獨：明知港獨冇可能，都硬碰。人大104條釋法唔俾你做議員。之後再等基本法23條通過拉晒你班柒頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聰明的非港豬：努力賺多些錢，等自己儲夠錢後，即移民"},{"pid":"4bc50d7817e7ffc81d46300ff790aa40f77333f8","tid":562720,"uid":123711,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bf3699008fd6bf6f16a38d743f78047a6ae9f12","tid":562720,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T07:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/153718_a688c88b6a2307c3133820cf524580c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F153718_a688c88b6a2307c3133820cf524580c4.png&h=a6318e92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/153720_6a39601e87028efa7181dcfc4adee53d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F153720_6a39601e87028efa7181dcfc4adee53d.png&h=650613a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/153721_8e934afcb69de206fc4914aa5c746c9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F153721_8e934afcb69de206fc4914aa5c746c9d.png&h=09531661&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc5f3eaa4421c240cea51dc0f3106b5ea6e69b15","tid":562720,"uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"4bc50d7817